articles.author: Carly Schreck
articles.title: Knik Charter becomes first of 3 Alaska schools to receive donated fitness center
articles.description: Gov. Mike Dunleavy — alongside fitness guru Jake Steinfeld — cut the ribbon Monday morning on a new fitness center at Knik Charter School.
articles.content:
WASILLA, Alaska (KTUU) - Gov. Mike Dunleavy alongside fitness guru Jake Steinfeld cut the ribbon Monday morning on a new fitness center at Knik Charter School.
